div.p:
The Third Predicament is of Quality.
In this Predicament are placed all Qualities,
whereof there are Four kinds; 1, Habit;
2, Natural Abilities; 3, Sensible Qualities;
4, Figures or Forms.

There be Three kinds of Conversion;
First, Simple, Secondly per Accidens:
Thirdly pur contra positionem.
